      • getItemFactory

        protected FolderItemFactory getItemFactory()
        Gets the data item factory for this item

        Returns null until the register(Hive, FolderCommon) method was called.

        The registry will be disposed when unregister() is called. There is no need to unregister items manually.

        Returns:
        the item factory used for this item
